snippet.title: Wormhole - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1893880/Wormhole/

Jump and dash across space as you race against time in this punishing, fast-paced platformer. Be careful where you land, as the path ahead is filled with portals that will send you back. Will you beat the clock and escape the loop?
